TextEng: I am a member of the city guard under Aribeth's command.
Me is member of city guard.
Goodbye.
Have you heard any rumors about where they might be?
Text: 그들이 어디 있을지에 대한 소문을 들은 적 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard anything at all about the creatures?
Text: 그 생명체들에 대해 뭐라도 들은 게 있어?

TextEng: Anything of interest I should know about in Blacklake?
Text: 검은호수에서 알아둘 만한 흥미로운 소식이 있나요?

TextEng: Do you hear stuff about where monsters is?
You hears anything about creatures, maybe?
Text: 괴물 얘기 들은 거 있나, 혹시?

TextEng: Something goin' on in Blacklake?
So, none of the nobles have reported seeing anything strange?
Text: 그럼, 아무 귀족도 이상한 걸 봤다고 신고하지 않았나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Maybe you have heard of someone who might know more? Someone who's acting strangely.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 더 잘 아는 사람 얘기를 들은 적은? 요즘 수상하게 구는 사람이라든가.

TextEng: So, nobody see strange stuff?
Text: 그럼, 아무도 이상한 거 못 봤나?

TextEng: Who is Meldanen?
Anyone you know of in the Blacklake district who needs help?
Text: 검은호수 지구에서 도움이 필요한 사람 알아?

TextEng: Are there any places of interest in the Blacklake district that I should visit?
Text: 검은호수 지구에서 가볼 만한 흥미로운 장소가 있어?

TextEng: Meldanen? Who Meldanen?
Me city guard. Anyone need help from city guard?
Text: 나 도시 경비대. 도움 필요한 사람 있나?

TextEng: You know good places to go here?
Text: 여기 가볼 만한 좋은 데 있나?

TextEng: Have you heard any leads on who might have been responsible for the 'accident'?
Text: 그 '사고'를 누가 저질렀는지 단서 들은 거 있나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Don't you find it sort of strange that the 'accident' happened as soon as the creatures made it into the city?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그 '사고'가 그 생명체들이 도시에 들어오자마자 일어났다는 게 이상하다고 생각하지 않나요?

TextEng: You know maybe who set monsters free?
Text: 괴물 풀어준 놈 누군지, 혹시 아나?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, telling me won't do any harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 말해도 해가 될 건 없잖아요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. Will hurt nobody.
I've been commanded to find the Waterdhavian creatures. Have you heard anything about them?
Text: 워터딥 생명체들을 찾으라는 명령을 받았어. 그것들에 대해 들은 게 있어?

TextEng: Me supposed to find Waterdeep monsters. You hear something?
Text: 나 워터딥 괴물 찾으래. 뭐 들었나?

TextEng: I want to ask you something else.
Me have other question.
I need some directions.
Me need directions.
Where is the nearest tavern?
Where is the nearest temple?
Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Text: 근처에 장비를 살 수 있는 곳이 있어?

TextEng: Are there any places of interest in the Blacklake district that I should visit?
Text: 검은호수 지구에서 가볼 만한 곳이 있어?

TextEng: Me look for place to drink.
Me look for temple.
Me need place to buy stuff.
Any place that has fun stuff?
Why is it closed off?
Why it closed?
You will let me pass or I'll get very angry, fool.
Text: 통과시켜, 안 그러면 화낼 거야, 멍청아.

TextEng: Me pass or me gets very mad with you.
Text: 나 지나가. 아니면 나 엄청 화낸다.

TextEng: Seeing as I am under Aribeth's personal command, you may want to re-think that tone.
Text: 내가 아리베스의 지휘하에 있는 걸 안다면, 말투를 고쳐보는 게 좋을 겁니다.

TextEng: Me under Aribeth's personal command, you. Speak nice.
Text: 나 아리베스의 직접 명령 받아. 말 곱게 해.

TextEng: Fine, I'm going.
Okay, me go.
That's right.
Yeah? So?
Let me through the gate, then.
Lets me through gate.
Who's Samuel?
Who Samuel?
<StartCheck>[Flirt]</Start> Yous can tell me, okay, handsome guy?
Text: <StartCheck>[유혹]</Start> 말해줄 수 있지, 응? 멋진 사람?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Flirt]</Start> Come now, handsome. You can tell little old me.
Text: <StartCheck>[유혹]</Start> 자, 잘생긴 분. 작은 나한테 말해줄 수 있잖아.
